text: The term EM3 may refer to : * Exploration Mission 3, or EM-3, a scheduled mission for NASA's Orion spacecraft * Echo Meter EM3, a handheld active bat detector manufactured by US company Wildlife Acoustics * e-M3, a test electric vehicle developed by Croatian company Rimac Automobili * EM-3, a proposed experimental British assault rifle, a precursor of the EM-2 rifle * EM3, or Electrician's Mate 3rd Class, an enlisted rate in the US Navy and US Coast Guard * EM3, a category for streaming pupils formerly used in education in Singapore
title: EM3
